parameters: Sato Mamoru

"With a building this big, it's no surprise there's an
elevator. But if I use it, they'll know I've broken in, so
I'll take the stairs."
Sato Mamoru

"With a building this big, it's no surprise there's an
elevator. But if I ride it, they'll know I've infiltrated.
I'll use the stairs instead."
Sato Mamoru

"Fire extinguishers and fire alarms, huh. There are
sprinklers on the ceiling too, seems like they're fully
prepared for fires."
Sato Mamoru

"It's a stove used for cooking. I bet this one's got pretty
good performance."
Woman'S Voice
"Hurry... please... I really don't want... to do this..."
Suzuki Go

"Don't panic like that!! I'm going to take a shower first!!
Have some tea and relax!! Hyahahahahaha!!"
Sato Mamoru

(No doubt about it, that voice is Suzuki's! So this place
really is Suzuki's house...!)
Sato Mamoru

(The voice is faint and hard to make out, but it sounds like
he's talking to someone. Could it be that he's speaking with
Makoto...?)
Sato Mamoru

(Damn it, Suzuki... what are you planning to do to Makoto! I
can't just stand by! I need to rescue her quickly...!)
Sato Mamoru

(No, I need to calm down... I want to rescue her right now,
but what am I supposed to do after barging in?)
Sato Mamoru

(Even if the person upstairs is Makoto, she entered this
house of her own free will.)
Sato Mamoru

(I don't know what circumstances she's under, but even if I
try to take her away, she might refuse at worst.)
Sato Mamoru

(Besides, there's a chance that there are different henchmen
from earlier. If I act carelessly, I might just make the
situation worse.)
Sato Mamoru

(Ideally, I need to find a way to get Makoto out of here
without them realizing it's me...!)
Sato Mamoru
(There's not much time. I have to hurry and rescue Makoto!)
